          </p>
          <ul
            class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-5 marker:text-[--color-text-dim] text-[--color-text-muted] text-[15px] leading-relaxed"
          >
            <li>
              Reimplemented Microsoft's Collections to prevent Large Object
